'''SK-42参考系'''（{{lang-en|SK-42 reference system}}）又称{{le|费奥多西·克拉索夫斯基|Feodosy Krasovsky|克拉索夫斯基}}1940[[参考椭球|椭球]]，是1942年[[苏联|苏联]]建立的坐标系，称为Systema koordinat（{{lang-ru|Система координат 1942 года}}），提供的参数与地心[[笛卡尔坐标系|笛卡尔坐标系]][[PZ-90|PZ-90]]相联系。<ref name="mazurova">{{cite journal|author1=E.M. Mazurova|author2=S.M. Kopeikin|author3=A.P. Karpik|title=Development of a terrestrial reference frame in the Russian Federation|volume=61 |issue=4 |journal=Studia Geophysica et Geodaetica |pages=616–638|bibcode=2017StGG...61..616M |year=2017 |doi=10.1007/s11200-015-1106-4}}</ref> 它被用于大地测量计算，特别是在军事测绘和确定国家边界方面。 
SK-42坐标系统是开发{{le|SK-63参考系统|SK-63 reference system}}的基础，SK-63参考系统主要是为民用和工业发展目的而建立和使用的。<ref name="mazurova">{{cite journal|author1=E.M. Mazurova|author2=S.M. Kopeikin|author3=A.P. Karpik|title=Development of a terrestrial reference frame in the Russian Federation|volume=61 |issue=4 |journal=Studia Geophysica et Geodaetica |pages=616–638|bibcode=2017StGG...61..616M |year=2017 |doi=10.1007/s11200-015-1106-4}}</ref>

克拉索夫斯基1940椭球体采用{{le|半长轴|semi-major axis}}（赤道半径）{{math|''a''}} 为6,378,245 m，反扁率 {{math|1/''f''}} 为298.3。<ref name="mazurova"/><ref>{{cite book|last1=Office|first1=United States Naval Observatory Nautical Almanac|last2=Office|first2=Great Britain Nautical Almanac|title=Explanatory Supplement to the Astronomical Almanac|date=2005|publisher=University Science Books|isbn=9781891389450|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=uJ4JhGJANb4C|language=en}}</ref>{{rp|220}}

